msgid "prereq_cloudflare_title"
msgstr "This add-on assumes you already use Cloudflare"

msgid "prereq_cloudflare_p"
msgstr "This add-on uses the Cloudflare API to fetch and compare rule configuration. Your domain should be proxied through Cloudflare. The Cloudflare Free plan is enough for what the add-on reads from the API."

msgid "free_tier_title"
msgstr "What the free add-on tier covers"

msgid "free_tier_hook"
msgstr "There is only one difference: whether you can roll back."

msgid "free_tier_item_1"
msgstr "Fetch Page Rules, Cache Rules, and related zone settings and review them in the CS-Cart admin."

msgid "free_tier_item_2"
msgstr "Show a diff between the last saved snapshot and the current live configuration (read-focused workflows)."

msgid "free_tier_note"
msgstr "Fetch and diff are enough on Free. Rolling back to the last working state, applying changes, purging cache, and keeping rollback-ready history are Pro."

